<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śākābdēravisiṁdhusannidhiyutē hēmā<unclear>bi</unclear>dhēvatsarē mārgē māsyasitē dvitīyadivasē vārē śubē
<lb n="2" break="no"/>paṁḍitē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bhāradvājakulōdbhavasya nṛpatē<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīnārasiṁhasya tē viṣṇō śrīkamaṭhadhipaya
<lb n="3"/>nitarāṁ ddīpadvayartthaṁ ggavā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> prādāśrīpurusōtmamākhyanṛpatēraiśvaryasaṁsiddhayē
<lb n="4"/>Ācaṁdrārkkamidaṁ suvutraphaladaṁ paṁccaśadatyadbutaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>cātu<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>vva<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ggaphalapradaṁ
<lb n="5"/>suvimalaṁ śrīkaryamātyaṁttikaṁ kalyāṇaṁ svayamātanōtu bhavata śrīkurmma
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nāthō hariḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākavaruṣaṁbulu 1279 nēṁṭi mārggasira bhauḷa dvitī
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yānu paṁḍitavārānta śrīkū<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>mmanāduni sannidini Akhaṁḍadīpadvayānaku bīra
<lb n="8" break="no"/>goṭṭāna śrīnarasiṁhyarāju bhārya lakmadēvi svabhīṣṭasiddhyartthamai Ēṁbhayi gō
<lb n="9" break="no"/>vulaku yeṁbhaI gaṁḍamāḍalu peṭṭenu dīpastaṁbhasahitamugānu I
<lb n="10"/>śrīkāryamu ĀcaṁdrārkkastāIgānu Ī kṣētramaṁdula śrīvaiṣṇavurakṣa
<lb n="11"/>śrī śrī śrī śrī śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied><note n="421-1">At the end of the inscription are engraved the figures of a conch, two umbrellas, a discus seated bull below them.</note>
</p>

